(2) if.. else statement
~> when condition is true it will exicuet if block and if condition become false it will exicuet else
    block.

    syntex: 
        if condition:
            statement
        else:
            statement
---------------------------------------
(3) elif statement:
~> when we have multipul condition to check we use elif statement but if first condition is true it will
    not going to check other condition it will exicuet first condition block 

    syntex: 
        if condition:
            statement

        elif condition:
            statement
        elif condition:
            statement
        elif condition:
            statement

        else:
            statement
---------------------------------------
(4) nested statement:
~> when we have one condition inside another condition we use nested statement

    if condition:
        if condition:
            statement
        else:
            statement
    else:
        if condition:
            statement
        else:
            statement
---------------------------------------
